/target
# P12-FIX-A: Cargo.lock IS committed for this workspace. It produces
# binary artifacts (ullm-gateway, ullm-tee) whose reproducibility and
# supply-chain integrity depend on the locked transitive-dep versions.
# CI's `cargo audit` and the `prod-binary strings check` both rely on
# the locked tree being byte-stable across runs.
*.pem
*.key

# Audit packet tarballs are generated artifacts produced by
# scripts/build_audit_packet.sh. They're large (~1 MB), filenames
# embed the git SHA, and they're easy to regenerate. Don't track.
audit-packet-*.tar.gz
.env
.vscode
.idea
node_modules
dist
pkg
*.wasm
__pycache__
*.pyc
.pytest_cache
.venv
